org.cougaar.planning.plugin.legacy
Interface ParameterizedPlugin

Deprecated. We use introspection and the Component Model to find and call setParameter(Object) now instead of setParameters(Vector). 

public interface ParameterizedPlugin

Plugin classes which implement ParameterizedPlugin may be passed a Vector of Strings to parameterize the instance between class instantiation and Plugin.initialize(). While it is up to each implementation to decide what to do with the parameters, the org.cougaar.core.plugin.* plugin classes all provide a protected getParameters() method which may be used by subclasses to retrieve the strings.
